## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **autoimmune 진정한 cure 없음** — 모든 FDA 약물이 symptomatic / disease-modifying 단계, 진정한 immune tolerance restoration 아님.
2. **biologics (mAbs) immunogenicity** — anti-drug antibody 형성 가능. quantum-VQE 의 small-molecule path 가 immunogenicity 우회 가능.
3. **JAK inhibitors black box warning** — 2021 FDA black box (cardiovascular events, malignancy, blood clots) for tofacitinib/baricitinib/upadacitinib. risk-benefit balance 중요.
4. **TNF inhibitors 부작용** — 결핵 reactivation / lymphoma risk. quantum-design drug 가 selectivity 향상 시 대안 가능.
5. **S1P receptor 부작용** — first-dose bradycardia / macular edema. selectivity (S1PR1/5 vs all) 가 ozanimod path.
6. **MS progression** — DMTs (disease-modifying therapies) 가 relapse rate 감소 단 progression 완전 stop 못함. neuroprotection / remyelination novel mechanism 필요.
7. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, autoimmune 임상 의미 한정.

